# base64_images.md

#### example


#### Data URI: 
```
data:image/png;base64,
```

#### Image Tag: 
```
<img alt="stop.png" src="data:image/png;base64,"/>
```

##### CSS Background:
```
background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,");
```
